{"tid":489112,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"MMA上IU斬獲大賞粉絲們唱歌慶祝 她的反應竟如此可愛","createTime":"2017-12-04T11:04:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-04T12:44:31.000Z","uid":34643,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"19ac564bc4fa381b0b7a5aa28ed97f4e3222d59d","tid":489112,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T11:04:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3ohs7NRo7z8XS2GWKA/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3ohs7NRo7z8XS2GWKA%2Fgiphy.gif&h=f2612091&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「祝你拿到大賞，大賞，恭喜！！」聽到粉絲們歡呼聲的IU也做出了十分可愛的反應。<br />\n<br />\n2017年MMA中，IU斬獲了年度3座大賞中的「年度最佳專輯賞」，發表獲獎感言時，IU多次提及自己的粉絲後援團「U愛娜」，可見對自己的粉絲有多喜愛。<br />\n<br />\n而第二天在IU「全國巡演」的上班路上就受到了粉絲們的熱烈歡迎，眾人們用生日歌的曲調唱著「祝你拿到大賞」，聽到大家歡呼聲的IU伴隨著歌聲扭動起來，舉起雙手轉了一圈，最後還鞠躬向路兩旁的粉絲們道謝。慢慢走入會場的IU一直揮手和粉絲們打招呼。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/610*500_86400_d428cbf2d34d440824932980f666c82c/static.koreastardaily.com/2017-12-04/100468-561137.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F610%2A500_86400_d428cbf2d34d440824932980f666c82c%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2017-12-04%2F100468-561137.jpg&h=93875480&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n還有粉絲問：「姐姐，昨天激動的哭了吧？」IU搖頭帥氣說：「沒有」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=H3lNQHj5mSQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DH3lNQHj5mSQ&d=NlbSeFomOcymNKJohLc7o%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=1fd6d9b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=H3lNQHj5mSQ</a>"},{"pid":"21908599ff4e9a073d464be2e43bf92196b63dbb","tid":489112,"uid":29702,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T11:47:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5c488e5db7329a5df2442a428fd9f0e5a05ae696","tid":489112,"uid":72076,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T11:55:51.000Z","msg":"正宗低B妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3717e231968869dc3716b1769a9fb02f6ec7132","tid":489112,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T12:44:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正宗低B妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}